title: Verify that detailed overview of files within the submitted zip archive that could not be processed are displaying in the File Not Processed tab when a CSV zip file with incorrect file format is placed in the ingress folder via sftp

steps.stepname: Click on the Data Quality menu header.
Navigate to the CSV Data Quality tab - File Not Processed tab.
Verify that specific issues, such as missing files or incorrect file formats, along with their associated error messages are displaying.
